dashboard_item_ids.name: Revenue By sales Teams
dashboard_item_ids.query:
SELECT
    t.name AS sales_team,
    COUNT(o.id) AS order_count,
    SUM(o.amount_total) AS total_revenue
FROM
    sale_order o
JOIN crm_team t ON o.team_id = t.id
GROUP BY
    t.name
ORDER BY
    total_revenue DESC
